Laravel ORM+MVC
-Artisan: CLI
-Illuminate (Composer 4)
-Homestead: VM w/Laravel
Uses Composer as package system.

 -Elixir: Assets
 -Scheduler: Tasks
 -Blade: Template
...

# System: Mongo xx + Laravel xx + PHP 7
sudo apt-get install php composer php-mbstring php-zip php-xml php-curl

# Bash
echo 'PATH="$HOME/.config/composer/vendor/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.profile
source ~/.profile

# Laravel
composer global require "laravel/installer"

laravel new gs
cd gs

# Run
php artisan serve --host=0.0.0.0 --port=8080

